          <article class="faq-item is-open">
            <h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faqAnswer1"
                id="faqQuestion1">Do I need to be home during the clean?<span class="faq-question__icon"
                  aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h3>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer1" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqQuestion1">
              <div>
                <p>No. Many customers arrange access using a key, lockbox or building concierge. Share the instructions
                  securely when booking and come home to the finished result.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqAnswer2"
                id="faqQuestion2">Who provides the products and equipment?<span class="faq-question__icon"
                  aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h3>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer2" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqQuestion2">
              <div>
                <p>Our cleaners can bring professional cleaning products. If possible, we ask customers to provide a
                  working vacuum and mop suited to their own floors. Let us know if that is not possible and we will
                  organise accordingly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqAnswer3"
                id="faqQuestion3">Can I request the same cleaner each time?<span class="faq-question__icon"
                  aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h3>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer3" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqQuestion3">
              <div>
                <p>We aim for consistency on recurring bookings and will keep the same cleaner where availability
                  allows. If a change is ever needed, we organise an experienced replacement and keep you informed by
                  email.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqAnswer4"
                id="faqQuestion4">How do recurring discounts work?<span class="faq-question__icon"
                  aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h3>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer4" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqQuestion4">
              <div>
                <p>Weekly and fortnightly Standard or Deep cleans receive 10% off. Every three weeks and every four
                  weeks receive 5% off. Your discount is applied automatically in the calculator and booking flow.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqAnswer5"
                id="faqQuestion5">Does End of Lease cleaning guarantee my bond?<span class="faq-question__icon"
                  aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h3>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer5" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqQuestion5">
              <div>
                <p>Bond decisions are made by your landlord or property manager, so no cleaner can control the final
                  outcome. Our service follows a detailed vacate checklist and includes re-clean support for eligible
                  items reported within seven days.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="faq-item">
            <h3><button class="faq-question" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqAnswer6"
                id="faqQuestion6">What if my plans change?<span class="faq-question__icon"
                  aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h3>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faqAnswer6" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqQuestion6">
              <div>
                <p>Contact us as early as possible. Changes made with less than 24 hours' notice may incur a fee because
                  that time has been reserved for your cleaner. We will always help find the best available option.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
